@startuml SaniHub-Event-Routing
title SaniHub — Flux Événementiel : Commande Client (Order-to-Cash)

participant "Dynamics 365\n(CRM)" as Dynamics
participant "TrueCommerce\n(EDI)" as TrueCommerce
participant "SaniHub\nAPI Gateway" as APIGateway
participant "SaniHub\nRouter" as Router
participant "SaniHub\nTransformer" as Transformer
participant "Message\nBroker" as Broker
participant "Infor M3\nConnector" as M3Connector
participant "Ortems\nConnector" as OortemsConnector
participant "Infor M3\n(ERP)" as M3
participant "Ortems\n(Planning)" as Ortems

== Flux : Création Commande Client ==

TrueCommerce ->> APIGateway: POST /api/v1/events/publish\n{type: CommandeClientRecue, payload: {...}}
note over APIGateway: Authentification OAuth 2.0\nRate limit check\nLog entry point

APIGateway ->> Router: Route decision?
note over Router: Décide routage\n(voir règles statiques)

Router ->> Transformer: Transform → canonical
Transformer ->> Transformer: TrueCommerce format → CommandeClient (canonical)
Transformer ->> Broker: Publie event\n{type: CommandeClientCree, correlation_id: CMD-12345, payload: {...}}

Broker ->> M3Connector: Subscribe: CommandeClientCree
Broker ->> OortemsConnector: Subscribe: CommandeClientCree

M3Connector ->> M3: Connecteur adapte\nCommandeClient → Format M3\nwrite via OData API
M3 -->> M3Connector: OK (200) + M3_OrderId
M3Connector ->> Broker: Publie event\n{type: CommandeClientM3Created, correlation_id: CMD-12345, m3_order_id: M3-87654}

OortemsConnector ->> Ortems: Connecteur adapte\nCommandeClient → Format Ortems\nwrite via API Ortems
Ortems -->> OortemsConnector: OK + Ortems_OrderId
OortemsConnector ->> Broker: Publie event\n{type: OdfCreated, correlation_id: CMD-12345, ortems_odf_id: ODF-555}

note over Broker: All events persisted\nin Event Store (async)\nwith correlation_id = CMD-12345

== Dashboard Traçabilité ==
Dynamics ->> APIGateway: GET /api/v1/events/CMD-12345
APIGateway -->> Dynamics: Retourne tous les events pour CMD-12345\n1. CommandeClientRecue (TrueCommerce)\n2. CommandeClientCree (canonical)\n3. CommandeClientM3Created (M3)\n4. OdfCreated (Ortems)

@enduml

